title: "Visiting Scholar at Ludwig-Maximilian University, Munich, Germany"
date: 2024-08-01
excerpt: "Starting as a Visiting scholar at LMU Munich."
image: /assets/images/lmu.jpg  # ou qualquer imagem relevante
categories: [news]
